## ⚙️ Tech Stack

### 💻 Frontend
- HTML, CSS, Bootstrap 5
- Netlify (for static hosting)

### 🔧 Backend
- Python, Flask
- Flask-Login (auth)
- Flask-Dotenv

### 🗃️ Database
- Azure Database for MySQL (for users, transactions, Zakat history)
- SQLAlchemy or MySQL Connector (for DB connection)

### ☁️ Cloud Integration
- Azure Blob Storage (for uploading CSVs or reports)
- Azure App Service (for Flask app hosting)

### 🏦 Banking API
- [Plaid API](https://plaid.com/docs) (for securely connecting real bank accounts)
- Plaid Python SDK
- Plaid Link JavaScript for frontend auth

---

## 🔐 Security
- All secrets (API keys, DB creds) stored in `.env` and added to `.gitignore`
- HTTPS enforced via Netlify and Azure
- SQL injection protected via parameterized queries

